{"tid":593824,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"騰訊好醫生》易鑫去年虧損擴至183億人幣","createTime":"2018-03-15T10:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T04:17:38.000Z","uid":13663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d479e234d34036ba98db996d6334ff234bc550b4","tid":593824,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:14:49.000Z","msg":"易鑫去年虧損擴至183億人幣<br />\n<br />\n【分析】 信報財經新聞 33分鐘前<br />\n0<br />\n【信報財經新聞】易鑫集團(02858)公布，截至去年12月底止全年業績，股東應佔虧損擴大至183.31億元(人民幣‧下同)，受可轉換可贖回優先股公允價值虧損增至176.98億元。2016年虧損14.01億元。<br />\n<br />\n去年每股虧損11.37元，不派息。<br />\n<br />\n期內，經調整營業利潤4.89億元，按年增長2.25倍；經調整淨利潤4.64億元，按年增長3.66倍。<br />\n<br />\n期內，收入39.06億元，按年增加1.62倍。<br />\n<br />\n入qq 我們信<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee04b030f9d5b7f0cc721150af6b0e65cad7e10d","tid":593824,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b28990e748e691af38df5d2e08f97e5522c04444","tid":593824,"uid":131323,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:21:16.000Z","msg":"1股先6蚊點樣蝕12蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b305d68da8493910e61c9b68feead9fc012c17c","tid":593824,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b28990e748e691af38df5d2e08f97e5522c04444","tid":593824,"uid":131323,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:21:16.000Z","msg":"1股先6蚊點樣蝕12蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:26:53.000Z","msg":"獨角獸概念你識春咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fbb05ab83560e2ad50dbeece34013f4d2809fca","tid":593824,"uid":55335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T10:43:49.000Z","msg":"由2016年的14.28億元增加11倍至2017年的177億元。該損失大幅增加是由於業務及公司估值持續快速增長。於上市日期，所有優先股自動轉換為普通股，因而2018年及往後，不會再產生可轉換可贖回優先股的公允價值損失。"},{"pid":"3a412e9a71819ea6f08421ae5c74fc5284bcd408","tid":593824,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T01:59:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720ad5857699e9a0666adc9bf06108de9bd0255f","tid":593824,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T02:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46419ea34f485562166f6d3a5171f1e5a24021d0","tid":593824,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T02:51:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664bfcf317bdc45cc68ec0f2113dcc1604588b9d","tid":593824,"uid":24544,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T03:43:25.000Z","msg":"易鑫正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d833a86db1a403d9f7a03b9b4b4826b8b16664","tid":593824,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"664bfcf317bdc45cc68ec0f2113dcc1604588b9d","tid":593824,"uid":24544,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T03:43:25.000Z","msg":"易鑫正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T03:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/16/115340_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F16%2F115340_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=57699c8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f11c8af411eae1fc9ad2b931ac7a733b1f0eab8","tid":593824,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T04:17:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}